h1 Buttons
h2 Predefined buttons
p To quickly use buttons you can use the pre-defined buttons of the theme.
h6 Usage
pre
  code
    header HTML
    p
      = '<a href="#" class="btn default">Default</a>'
      br
      = '<a href="#" class="btn primary">Primary</a>'
      br
      = '<a href="#" class="btn success">Success</a>'
      br
      = '<a href="#" class="btn info">Info</a>'
      br
      = '<a href="#" class="btn warning">Warning</a>'
      br
      = '<a href="#" class="btn danger">Danger</a>'
      br
      = '<a href="#" class="btn link">Link</a>'
      br
h6 Output
.example
  a.btn.default href="#" Default
  a.btn.primary href="#" Primary
  a.btn.success href="#" Success
  a.btn.info href="#" Info
  a.btn.warning href="#" Warning
  a.btn.danger href="#" Danger
  a.btn.link href="#" Link

